title: Unable to connect to the authentification service.
body:
Hello Guy's.
Is there a maintenance on EUW servers at the moment ?
Servers seem to be all up and ready but still can't connect.

replies.body: Ah, it looks like there was an unexpected maintenance per the [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.  Keep an eye out, and it should be resolved in about 3 hours per the status.
Yea...it always happend to me aswell.
